1. d4 d5 2. Nc3 Nf6 3. Bf4 { The Jobava has become quite popular and can be tricky to deal with. But it's actually pretty easy to neutralize if you know what you're doing. } 3... e6 { I think this is the easiest response to learn. Getting ready to bring out the bishop, pinning the knight on c3 if possible, and castle kingside quickly. White has two main responses... } { [%cal Gf8b4,Ge8g8,Gc7c5] } *


